Five-time Grammy winner Ladysmith Black Mambazo is set to perform in tribute to Madiba. Theodor Mashele has this story for us. #DStv403 JOHANNESBURG - Five-time Grammy winner Ladysmith Black Mambazo is set to perform in tribute to Madiba. It has been nine years since the passing of our former president Tata Nelson Mandela. Dedicated to celebrating the life and times of the world-renowned political icon, the concert will feature classic Mambazo hits as well as new music from the Acapela group. The concert will take place at The Joburg Theatre in Braamfontein on 17 July. * Theodor Mashele reports.